		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Visual language</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>A <b>visual language</b> is a set of practices by which <a href="/wiki/Image" title="Image">images</a> can be used to <a href="/wiki/Communication" title="Communication">communicate</a> <a href="/wiki/Concept" title="Concept">concepts</a>.</p>
